@startuml context-map-detailed
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #78909C
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam componentBorderColor #78909C
skinparam cloudBorderColor #78909C
skinparam actorBorderColor #37474F
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #BDBDBD
skinparam ArrowColor #546E7A
skinparam ArrowFontColor #37474F
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11

actor "End user" as User
cloud "Binance feeds\n(external market source)" as Binance #FFF3E0
cloud "Camunda 8\norchestration" as Camunda #E3F2FD

rectangle "CryptoFlow platform" as Platform #F5F5F5 {
    component "market-data-service" as MD #FFF8E1
    component "user-service" as US #FCE4EC
    component "onboarding-service" as ONB #EDE7F6
    component "transaction-service" as TR #E3F2FD
    component "portfolio-service" as PF #E8F5E9
}

note bottom of Platform
  **shared-events** module
  Kafka event contracts shared by
  market-data, user, transaction, portfolio
end note

Binance --> MD
User --> Camunda : Tasklist forms

MD --> TR : crypto.price.raw
MD --> PF : crypto.price.raw
US -left-> TR : user.confirmed\n(compacted)
TR -right-> PF : transaction.order.approved
US --> PF : crypto.portfolio.compensation
PF --> US : crypto.user.compensation

ONB .up.> Camunda : deploys userOnboarding
TR ..> Camunda : deploys placeOrder
Camunda ..> US : onboarding jobs
Camunda ..> PF : onboarding jobs
Camunda ...> TR : order jobs

@enduml
